snippet.title: Diner Bros - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Now Available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/846800/Diner_Bros/

Diner Bros. is a hectic cooking and restaurant management game. Cook and serve the meals as fast as you can, but don’t get the orders wrong or your customers will be angry – and hungry! Upgrade your restaurant to get new recipes and hire staff to help you serving… or play with your friends in 2-4 player couch co-op action!
